## Meta

Prefer scripts over AI guidance; use natural language only where code cannot.

## Structure

### Manual
Self-contained for a human — steps, configure table, then reference Build.

### Automated
Claude drives via tmux. Ask first → Run → Report.

### DRY
Shared content lives in Manual. Automated references it, never duplicates.

### Run
Canonical execution — tmux commands, before/build/after. Referenced by both.

### Report
Component, machine, directory, branch, steps run, errors, next step.
